<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>归终百科 · Arseeya</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c1f, #1a1a2e);
            color: #eee;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .navbar a {
            color: #ddd;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .navbar a:hover {
            background: #e94560;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e94560, #667eea);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .category-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .category-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        .category-card:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }
        .category-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }
        .category-card h2 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #e94560;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }
        .category-card p {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #aaa;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #aaa;
        }
        footer a {
            color: #aaa;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        footer a:hover {
            color: #e94560;
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .category-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="navbar">
        <a href="index.html">首页</a>
        <a href="/novels/%E5%90%AC%E6%BD%AE%E4%BA%8B%E8%AE%B0/">作品</a>
        <a href="world.html">百科</a>
        <a href="download.html">下载</a>
        <a href="paid.html">付费项目</a>
    </div>

    <h1>📜 归终百科</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">记录世界的每一片潮汐</div>

    <div class="category-grid">
        <a href="world_characters.html" class="category-card">
            <div class="category-icon">🌊</div>
            <h2>人物</h2>
            <p>角色档案 · 待完善</p>
        </a>
        <a href="world_history.html" class="category-card">
            <div class="category-icon">📖</div>
            <h2>历史</h2>
            <p>时间线 · 待完善</p>
        </a>
        <a href="world_locations.html" class="category-card">
            <div class="category-icon">📍</div>
            <h2>地点</h2>
            <p>地域介绍 · 待完善</p>
        </a>
        <a href="world_knowledge.html" class="category-card">
            <div class="category-icon">💡</div>
            <h2>知识</h2>
            <p>世界观设定 · 待完善</p>
        </a>
    </div>

    <footer>
        © Arseeya. All Rights Reserved | <a href="terms.html">📜 完整条款</a>
    </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>